jobs.content:
&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coinbase Canada is looking for a highly motivated accounting and finance professional to join our Global Controllership team and play a key role in our continued growth and achievement of operational excellence. The Accounting and Reporting Manager, Canada must possess strong accounting, finance, operational and managerial expertise, an ability to communicate and work with various teams inside of Finance (such as Tax, FP&amp;amp;A, Financial Reporting, Treasury, Payroll and Accounts Payable), and a desire to make a meaningful impact on a dynamic, high-growth technology company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Global Assistant Controller, the Accounting and Reporting Manager, Canada will play a pivotal role in overseeing and managing portions of Coinbase Global’s operational finance and accounting tasks as well as ensuring adherence to the nuanced regulatory framework outlined by the Canadian Securities Administration (CSA) for Crypto Trading Platforms (CTPs) and National Instrument 31-103. The position is designed for a highly-technical individual and will involve collaborating with a multi-national controllership organization. This position will directly own the maintenance of the books of account under IFRS and will also include involvement in the month-end close process including preparing and/or reviewing accounting reconciliations and analyses. The role will require collaboration with various teams across the organization to ensure the complete and accurate delivery of reporting to&amp;nbsp; senior management and the board of director. This role will also play a crucial role in process design to include assisting with the implementation of controls and process improvements. This role requires someone with impeccable attention to detail, a financial and analytic mindset, and a strong desire to develop their career at a rapidly growing organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overseeing the accounting, financial and regulatory reporting and finance functions in Canada and ensuring finance processes operate effectively and accurately, following the Coinbase centralized model,&amp;nbsp; delivering accurate financial insights into the business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partnering with the Global accounting team to prepare and/or review assigned month end and quarter end close book close processes, own the Company’s parallel books of accounts maintained in line with IFRS and maintain appropriate reconciliations and valid support for all adjustments.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for preparation and coordination of financial statements, regulatory reporting,&amp;nbsp; business forecasts (partnering with FP&amp;amp;A) and other related information for external use (audit, submission to regulators, etc.), and play a leading role in external communication as the representative of the Finance department.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preparation of Coinbase Canada monthly management reporting and analytical review thereof, including reporting and communication to the Board.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as a contact point within the company for financial and accounting queries and queries from regulatory authorities relating to the finance function of the firm.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preparing and updating various finance policies and procedures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitoring and overseeing the performance of outsourced services by outsourced service providers relating to the finance function and assessing KPIs and SLAs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Active in Coinbase Canada liquidity management and&amp;nbsp; coordinating closely with the treasury team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participating&amp;nbsp; in critical projects, including the transitioning to new external vendors, integration, automation or enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting ad hoc financial information requests and analyses and other special projects as assigned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years’ experience as a finance professional at a bank, fin-tech, financial regulatory agency and/or professional service firm serving financial institution clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ experience working in a regulated entity/environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous Board/senior management level experience, or demonstrated the ability to communicate directly to the Board/senior management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CPA or equivalent required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work collaboratively with a broad range of business functions, with an emphasis on senior management and a track record of performing in a management role. Project management experience is essential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication – fluency in English is a key requirement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capacity to meet deadlines while maintaining quality standards and effective time management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to thrive in a fast-paced environment within a high growth business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert knowledge and experience with IFRS and&amp;nbsp; US GAAP.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of accounting month-end book close process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills, both written and verbal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working in Netsuite, FloQast and Google Suite.Experience working in a SOX control environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of digital assets and the crypto economy, or a desire to learn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of SQL and experience working with Snowflake, Looker or similar analytics tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job #: P56505&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice: &lt;/strong&gt;The target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, and vision).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$165,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$165,000 CAD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The International Policy Team sits in the overall Policy Team within the Trust &amp;amp; Risk Department at Coinbase. The International Policy Team engages with global policymakers to shape informed and effective crypto regulations worldwide. Our approach is guided by our Go Deep and Go Broad international strategy, which ladders up to our company wide ambition to help onboard the next billion users into crypto.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct policy and legislative research that reflects the policy team’s priorities and contributes to critical policy outcomes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and recommend proactive strategies on policy issues affecting Coinbase in&amp;nbsp; the Americas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the Policy team on regulatory whitepapers, consultations, and thought leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as an interface for government relationships in Canada and Latin America alongside country management.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage on legislative and industry issues that impact the company’s reputation with policymakers in relevant countries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop position papers and advocacy documents to support advocacy goals, align policy positions across key functions, and ensure consistency in messaging across the company on core policy issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and analyze policy trends for the company; succinctly synthesize information for internal audiences on potential legislation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional colleagues on&amp;nbsp; external policy communications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross functional collaboration to strategically support the company’s international expansion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Know-how in the area of financial services and / or technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated experience engaging and effectively interacting with lawmakers and regulators.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience advising Product and Engineering teams to consider and operationalize policy considerations as part of their business roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Superlative research, writing and communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enthusiasm for working on novel issues in a turbocharged environment, combined with a bias for proactive collaboration when problem solving.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong interest in digital assets, crypto markets, and blockchain technology.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High-EQ and a passion for acting like an owner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spanish and / or Portuguese language skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work experience in a legislature or financial regulator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job #: P56179&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice:&lt;/strong&gt; Depending on your work location, the target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, vision and 401(k)).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range: &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$184,025&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$216,500 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coinbase’s Asia Pacific Institutional Operations Solutions team provides 24x7 support to customers of the Institutional Business during APAC hours. Team members rotate their focus across multiple functional disciplines, including Treasury, Trading Execution Services, Prime and Exchange Client Services, and play a crucial role in the success of the firm’s global business.&amp;nbsp;As a relatively small team, each individual is expected to work closely with local management to ensure appropriate support for each function across the wider team. With a broad set of functions present, team-members will be presented with many opportunities to develop technical and functional skills to the level of a subject matter expert.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key member of the global 24x7 Operating Model for Institutional Operations Solutions; balancing product expertise &amp;amp; client management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform crypto and fiat movement, reporting activities and inventory management to facilitate critical client relationships, internal flows and the rebalancing of external trading venues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Settle OTC (over-the-counter) trades with counterparties and work with other support teams to troubleshoot trading related issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide direct client service &amp;amp; support to global institutional clients via phone, chat,&amp;nbsp; email &amp;amp; video calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate prospect and client demo calls, serving as subject matter specialist on our Institutional product suite of services and answering technical cryptocurrency related questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive impactful changes across workflows &amp;amp; tools through partnership with Sales, Engineering, Compliance, Tooling &amp;amp; Product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage effective project management, conclusive prioritization and efficient execution skills to deliver again job responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to cross-functional projects spanning multiple months with direct alignment to organizational OKRs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help to serve as the voice of the customer to internal cross-functional teams, including Program Management, Engineering and Product when surfacing bugs, incidents and product feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to be part of a 24/7 support rotation with a global team, including weekend coverage on a rotational basis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Professional experience coupled with strong operational background and the ability to multitask will be critical&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of financial markets and related instruments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with cryptocurrencies including exchange trading and blockchain transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid regulatory background and strong risk awareness&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail, problem solving/analytical abilities, and research skills in a fast pace constantly evolving working environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fantastic communication skills in order to operate across multiple departments, stakeholders, and clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge and understanding of derivatives and structured products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;P55879&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
