&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team/ Role Paragraph:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a seasoned Business Systems Analyst to support the Enterprise Integrations Team, gathering technical requirements at the beginning of the integration project lifecycle so that engineers don’t have to spend as much time on discovery and analysis before writing code. This person should have a passion for data and efficient execution to deliver business value by unlocking seamless and secure communications across our SaaS ecosystem and will have experience documenting functional and non-functional requirements for integration projects. A successful candidate will have previous experience reviewing PRDs, vendor API documentation, and hands-on experience capturing field mapping details.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and document the integration requirements for enterprise systems, to ensure the delivery of system integrations, APIs, and data services that align with business objectives and expectations of business stakeholders in Finance, HR, Compliance, Customer Experience, and other business functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product Managers, fellow Business System Analysts, and Engineers to clarify and capture the functional and non-functional integration requirements and create user acceptance testing scenarios.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and discover integration capabilities of enterprise applications using documentation, postman or soapUI, or by running SQL queries in Snowflake, Postgres or similar databases to better understand data fields, tables and columns for the purpose of designing data transformation and creating mapping specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the project hand-off to the engineering teams and work with engineers to drive delivery through clear acceptance criteria in Feature Stories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain the integration catalog with definitions and data objects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with stakeholders to triage new software integration and enhancement requests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act with a solutioning mindset to proactively create and enhance the business capabilities provided by Coinbase business systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in Agile ceremonies, perform the sprint reviews with stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of overall experience working in complex cross functional initiatives as a Business Analyst/Product Owner with prior technical background&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with large scale enterprise platforms (i.e., NetSuite, Salesforce, Anaplan, Workday etc.) with in-depth understanding of how systems interface with each other (REST, SOAP, GraphQL)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience as an engineer preferably on iPaaS solutions such as MuleSoft, Workato or similar integration platforms and tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp; in ETL/data warehouse technologies and running SQL queries&amp;nbsp; with the knowledge of data transformation, data mappings, and scrubbing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in automating diverse business processes using Business Process Automation, Robotics Process Automation, and Generative AI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in requirement gathering &amp;amp; analysis, translation into understandable &amp;amp; detailed functional requirements/non-functional requirements/user stories needed to build interfaces between systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A great communicator and can build relationships with a diverse set of stakeholders, including both technical and non-technical partners in order to drive alignment and assess completeness of requirements information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in Agile Development, Scrum &amp;amp; Kanban methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self starter with demonstrated ability to create order out of chaos, with great organizational skills and minimal oversight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quick learner, and able to work in a dynamic, fast paced and often changing environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adapt and be effective working with local, remote, global team members in global time-zones&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work on multiple features and projects in parallel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in engineering or software developer roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of Cloud Infrastructure, and any programming language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced understanding of G-Suite, Slack, Jira, and LeanIX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgeable and passionate about cryptocurrency and blockchain&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PID : P55719&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Coinbase is looking for a highly motivated accounting professional to join the Controllership team to lead the accounting and reporting for all futures and derivatives products for both regulated and non-regulated entities, and serve as the Chief Financial Officer for our US based regulated FCM, Coinbase Financial Markets. The ideal candidate must possess strong accounting, compliance, regulatory reporting and operational expertise, an ability to communicate and work with various teams outside of Finance (such as Legal/Compliance, Trading Operations and other Product/Engineering groups), and a desire to make a significant impact on a dynamic, high-growth technology company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Global Corporate Controller, the CFO &amp;amp; Head of Regulatory Accounting, Coinbase Financial Markets will be responsible for the daily monitoring, accounting, reporting and analysis of business activity related to derivatives and financial instruments at Coinbase and all regulatory compliance requirements related to the registered FCM. This position will work with various cross functional teams within the Company and requires someone with impeccable attention to detail, a financial and analytic mindset and knowledge of accounting for derivatives and financial instruments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for oversight, review and timely submission of all required reporting to the CFTC, NFA and other regulatory agencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for leading a team through all aspects of monthly accounting close activities related to derivatives for regulated and non-regulated entities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the preparation of monthly financial statements and quarterly/annual financial results presentations and board meeting materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with leadership in various operations and trading teams in the development and monitoring of hedging programs and trading strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design and implementation of internal controls over compliance, regulatory reporting and accounting policies and procedures&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor the firm’s daily liquidity management and capital requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate all internal and external audits for the registered FCM entity and non-regulated derivatives trading entities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BS in Accounting or related field / CPA required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NFA Series 3 license required, FINRA series 24, 27 or equivalent licenses nice to have&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 10 years experience in in a combination of public accounting, FCM and broker-dealer industry with an emphasis on accounting, financial management and regulatory reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of Futures Exchange / CFTC / NFA Rules and Regulations as they apply to a registered Futures Commission Merchant and ability to apply regulations to new situations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience interacting with regulators such as FINRA, NFA, CFTC and ability to respond to regulatory inquiries and lead routine compliance examinations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical understanding of customer asset protection standards, margin requirements, and both operational and financial regulatory reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of accounting guidance related to Derivatives and Hedging (ASC 815) and customer fund protection guidance related to FCM futures clients (17 CFR 1.20)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgeable about investments with an interest in blockchain technology and cryptocurrency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to maintain a deep understanding and remain current with the applicable federal and state securities laws and regulations; along with SRO rules relating to financial and operational responsibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert project management skills and ability to manage numerous projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, ability to collaborate effectively with team members and business stakeholders, and promptly escalate material issues to internal stakeholders and/or regulators as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exhibit solid analytical thinking, ability to work in a fast-paced, rapidly changing&amp;nbsp; environment with excellent prioritization and organizational skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have the ability to work EST hours to meet daily regulatory filing deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working at a publicly traded company&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of SQL, Python or other programming languages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in Netsuite, WinJammer, ION XTP, FloQast and G-Suite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PID: P54625&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice:&lt;/strong&gt; Depending on your work location, the target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, vision and 401(k)).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range: &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$161,500&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$190,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Chief Compliance Officer will directly support Coinbase Asset Management and will be part of the Coinbase Institutional Compliance team, which supports all products and business lines within Coinbase Institutional, including: Prime Brokerage, Custody, Derivatives Exchange, Futures Commission Merchant, Market Health and Monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting in capacity of Chief Compliance Officer of Coinbase Asset Management (“CBAM”), a Registered investment Adviser with the SEC&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for continued build out of CBAM’s compliance program, which includes: advising the business, developing policies, reviewing marketing materials, performing annual compliance testing, establishing training programs and coordinating all mandatory filings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaising with Institutional Compliance team members, Legal and Operations staff, and other cross-functional partners in daily support of CBAM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in supporting registered investment advisers in a senior compliance officer role, with 3+ years as a CCO or equivalent&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for building a world class compliance program for the leading company in the crypto industry&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working autonomously in a fast paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in the crypto space&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with compliance requirements of foreign jurisdictions (e.g.; Cayman Islands and the UAE)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Law degree&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job #: P56190&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice:&lt;/strong&gt; Depending on your work location, the target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, vision and 401(k)).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range: &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$245,225&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$288,500 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;On the institutional side of our business, some of the world’s most sophisticated clients have chosen Coinbase’s industry leading Prime offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are growing our Institutional Trading team and are looking for motivated people to help chart the path of a new and rapidly expanding business. If you have a positive, proactive, startup mentality, and are interested in joining a highly disruptive business on the forefront of the burgeoning cryptocurrency industry, then you’ve come to the right place.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our institutional clients are both “crypto-forward” and traditional asset managers such as asset managers, hedge funds, VCs, family offices, pensions and endowments. You will be part of a team that cultivates key customer relationships in the US and abroad. This role is embedded in the Global Trading team, and will help develop and execute the strategies to deliver on some of Coinbase’s key growth objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive increased trading volume to Coinbase&#39;s Execution Desk by understanding clients&#39; liquidity needs, proactively identify ways for high and low touch execution services to meet those needs, and provide client support for execution, liquidity, and market color.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain relationships with clients trading through quality execution and service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with the Sales, Financing and Account Management teams to identify, onboard, and monetize new client relationships and proactively identify new business opportunities for Coinbase.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide market color to clients on market conditions with an emphasis on liquidity and flow thematics and build trust through daily interactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a pulse on the sentiment, trading activity, and provide feedback from client base and marketplace and keep relevant internal teams informed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist institutional Product Managers by providing feedback from clients to help guide new product development that meets client&#39;s needs in both the spot trading business and financing business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;While Coinbase is generally remote-first, this role is located in NYC and will be required to work from our NYC office at least 3 days a week.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Weekend work is expected&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ year(s) of Sales and/or Trading experience in digital assets, FX, equities, credit or derivatives at a top tier institution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong quantitative skills&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Counterparty relationship management: ability to build and maintain strong relationships with counterparties.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with daily execution of trading and settlement functions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of risk management and ability to implement this knowledge well.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial mindset with a desire to build businesses from the ground up.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong data analysis, relationship management, and interpersonal communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can-do attitude and willingness to work hard and be scrappy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent numerical, verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to make informed decisions in fast-paced trading environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Intellectual curiosity and a passion for markets and/or crypto and digital assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Existing experience with institutions trading digital assets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced excel&amp;nbsp; or python skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
