&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Trade Surveillance Associate will be responsible for communication/trade surveillance for Coinbase on an ongoing basis. This person will help the Trade Surveillance team monitor markets, investigate any suspicious trading behavior, and lever various surveillance technologies to help keep Coinbase the most trusted platform in the space. This position will be remote but should anticipate some travel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct daily, weekly and monthly monitoring of e-comms/voice/trade surveillance and develop and implement surveillance reports as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and investigate alerts generated by surveillance systems and properly escalate as necessary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in new asset launches and monitoring market depth and liquidity relative to other assets and exchanges; perform market assessments for new asset launches and relaunches following trading halts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform other aspects of Compliance, where needed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep abreast of regulatory and market structure changes that may affect our markets and the scope of the existing surveillance program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with engineering and support staff to create process efficiencies and improvements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enforce and enhance policies and procedures related to Coinbase Trading operations and Trading Rules&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with Coinbase personnel related to Coinbase Trading Policies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with other key compliance individuals and separate Coinbase business lines on compliance investigations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on ad-hoc inquiries, special projects, or regulatory requests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 2+ years relevant experience in markets/ecomms surveillance or trading capacity&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive knowledge of applicable laws, regulations, and guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent analytical and critical reasoning skills, and a quick learner; demonstrate Coinbase values&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of market structure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross functional experience as well as proficient with creation and management of policies and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to act like an owner, i.e. manage and drive projects and seek continuous improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to problem solve and excel in a fast paced environment&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of blockchain, cryptocurrency ecosystems, and DeFi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FINRA Series or other relevant certifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of related Compliance functions (e.g. AML, Employee Compliance)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to query and manage data (e.g. SQL)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job #: P55411&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice:&lt;/strong&gt; Depending on your work location, the target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, vision and 401(k)).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range: &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$105,400&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$124,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/