&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Base’s mission is to build a global onchain economy that increases innovation, creativity, and economic freedom.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We believe that the onchain platform is the most important builder platform since the internet (“online”). We believe that the onchain platform should be open source, free to use, and globally available. And we believe that in order to make it really work, we need all hands on deck, working together to scale in a secure, decentralized, easy-to-use way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Base is incubated within Coinbase and plans to progressively decentralize in the years ahead. We believe that decentralization is critical to creating an open, global cryptoeconomy that is accessible to everyone.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Base is built on Optimism’s open-source OP Stack. We’re joining as the second Core Dev team working on the OP Stack to ensure it’s a public good available to everyone; and contributing a portion of sequencer revenue to funding public goods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Base is looking for a passionate Consumer Ecosystem Associate who will help us build the onchain creative future. You’ll work with the engineering, product, and creative teams to realize Base’s mission of building a global onchain economy. If you are excited by our mission, please apply and get in touch.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute strategic initiatives that position Base as the preferred network for creators, brands, developers and users.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain productive relationships with partners, establishing shared KPIs and resolving business, policy and technical issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide recommendations for expansion opportunities that have a direct impact on product roadmaps and business goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross functionally with key stakeholders to optimize builder programs and experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years relevant experience in technology, crypto, investing, banking or consulting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An unrelenting passion for the onchain media (e.g. social, games, creators, etc.) and a robust onchain resume&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A results-driven mindset with humility and self-awareness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of driving positive partner experiences while properly setting expectations and holding difficult conversations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing multiple complex projects across internal and external stakeholders through clear communication, strong analytical skills (qualitative and quantitative), and a constant focus on operational excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience scaling a product, process, or idea to a developer community.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
