&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an Engineering Leader to join Trust &amp;amp; Loyalty to lead a brand new team focused on high net worth individuals (HNW). This new team will work very closely with the broader Coinbase One (CB1) team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CB1 redefines what it means to be a member of the crypto community by providing an array of unparalleled benefits like zero trading fees, boosted staking rewards, account protection, and priority support to members. Our vision is to create the Amazon Prime experience for all Coinbase users, by creating a membership that users can&#39;t afford not to get, and becomes a reason users choose Coinbase over all other competitors.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an Engineering Manager of the HNW team, you&#39;ll play a pivotal role in creating unique experiences and value to our customers that drive the largest revenue for Coinbase (think elevated in-app delight to white-glove services such as account managers &amp;amp; VIP support). You’ll work closely with your product partner to define a business, product, and engineering strategy to launch + scale this brand new effort.&lt;/p&gt;
