&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;fn4is&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;9v5ct-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;9v5ct-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The mission of the Platform Product Group engineers is to build a trusted, scalable and compliant platform to operate with speed, efficiency and quality. Our teams build and maintain the platforms critical to the existence of Coinbase. There are many teams that make up this group which include Product Foundations (i.e. Identity, Payment, Risk, Proofing &amp;amp; Regulatory, Finhub), Machine Learning, Customer Experience, and Infrastructure.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work in a small team to iteratively improve user experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take new features from ideation, to prototyping, to user testing, to production&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design web and mobile experiences that are simple and intuitive&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in regular design reviews where you’ll seek out specific feedback on your designs and incorporate relevant feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute on the product roadmap and help define product strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Daily collaboration with Engineering, User Research, and Product&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of professional Product Design experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing consumer-facing experiences for web and mobile&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellence in UX thinking, visual design, and written communication&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in a collaborative environment with engineers, user researchers, and product teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in Figma and prototyping tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Low ego, collaborative, and open minded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interest in crypto or financial products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;User of Coinbase products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ID: GP854IN&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team/ Role Paragraph:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Enterprise Applications &amp;amp; Architecture (EAA) Team acts as a catalyst for Coinbase by using best-in-class, 3rd-party, enterprise applications; purpose-built software; automation; and integrated workflows – all of which free associates’ minds and time to focus on high-judgment tasks. The Business Unit Delivery team is a vital part of Coinbase’s Enterprise Applications and Architecture org, responsible for building and supporting applications used by our business unit partners on a daily basis to perform their work tasks. The CXP team within Business Unit Delivery is responsible for building, configuring and managing applications to drive best-in-class customer service for Coinbase customers, through enabling an efficient and effective customer service network.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a product manager to our team who will be responsible for integrating home-grown and third party generative AI solutions with our existing, as well as under-development Customer Service applications used by our Customer Service Agents (e.g. Continuously improve Coinbase’s internal LLM with new knowledge bases targeted for various Customer Service network personas, Integrate Coinbase’s internal LLM-based Agent Assist product with both Salesforce Case Management Experience and Coinbase’s internally built Compliance Case Handling product). This product manager will also be responsible for driving various initiatives to implement and optimize the use of third party tools, used within our Customer Service Agent network (e.g. Amazon Connect, SFDC, Voice of the Customer tools). For example, the product manager is going to partner with SFDC and internal Customer Service operations teams to optimize the use of SFDC for agents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As part of this role, you will create and synthesize a product vision into key technical decisions and partner daily with non-technical and technical business partners across many teams at Coinbase including, Product, Engineering, Machine Learning, Customer Service Operations, Compliance, and Security. You will develop user personas and define and prioritize use cases for each persona to build a backlog and a roadmap for the applications you will be working on. You will work with teams across Coinbase to identify the technical owners of various knowledge bases applicable for CX Agents, partner with them and the CB ML team to integrate these knowledge bases with CB’s LLM. You have solid working product, design and technical skills to build and deliver simple and intuitive products. You also have experience working with third party SaaS applications like Amazon Connect, SFDC. You possess the versatility to understand your stakeholder challenges and translate these into technical requirements for the engineering team. You will report to a Group Product Manager on a team of Product Managers and Technical Program Managers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively builds relationships with key stakeholders to understand each team’s scope and requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop user personas and define and prioritize use cases for each persona to build a backlog and a roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure the ‘What’ and ‘Why’ of every tool or feature is clearly defined, documented and communicated to engineering partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop user journey maps and process documentation for users of the product.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build an expert understanding of the customer journey for your stakeholders (both process and systems) and identify key pain points or areas of opportunity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and articulate vision for product development to support our internal customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively communicate with all levels of staff, including executive level stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure Engineering teams have 4-6 weeks worth of refined backlog.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct Demos to business users of capabilities completed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run User Acceptance Testing and Sign-off on behalf of the business, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan and coordinate across multiple engineering teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spearhead change management activities to drive successful adoption of capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and analyze metrics and KPIs that mature the Product Management function.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA/BS, preferably in Engineering, Computer Sciences, or Business Administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years experience, preferably in business applications development or product management for internal products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with and configuring third party SaaS applications (e.g. Amazon Connect, Salesforce) and third-party vendor software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in delivering features to end users through Generative AI and LLMs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with both back-end API infrastructure projects and integrations, and front-end product development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working across large, complex, cross-functional business units (Product &amp;amp; Engineering, Compliance, Legal, Machine Learning, Customer Support).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to surface and resolve tough trade-offs decisions and prioritization based on data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience tackling complex, ambiguous technical challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background working within an Agile environment and using Jira.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with financial institutions and entities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience driving RFP processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job #: P56527&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice:&lt;/strong&gt; Depending on your work location, the target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, vision and 401(k)).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range: &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$162,350&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$191,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;6rt44-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;1npem-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;1npem-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Coinbase Canada is the easiest, safest, and most trusted crypto currency exchange in Canada. We’re seeking a dynamic Product Manager to own our product experience for Canadians. At Coinbase, we&#39;re committed to building an open, accessible, and transparent financial system, tailored specifically for the Canadian market. This role offers an unparalleled opportunity to be at the forefront of shaping the future of finance and blockchain technology in Canada, in a company that values trust, equality, and regulatory foresight.&amp;nbsp; &lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;4iede-0-0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;6vv09-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;6vv09-0-0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-ul&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Own product development for Coinbase Canada&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Define and analyze metrics that inform the success of products&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Understand Coinbase Canada’s market opportunity and bring compliant, innovative products to Canadians &amp;nbsp;from conception to launch. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with engineering, design and cross-functional teams to develop and steer product roadmap&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Define and analyze metrics to guide product development&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Align teams on a shared vision and steer execution on that vision.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;337hi-0-0&quot;&gt;Communicate progress on initiatives to cross-functional partners and executive leadership&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8t66-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8t66-0-0&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;8t66-0-0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-ul&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;5+ years of product management experience&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;Exceptional interpersonal communication, relationship management and organizational skills&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;Deep analytical, prioritization and problem solving skills&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;Previous experience working in software product management&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;Demonstrated passion for cryptocurrency, financial markets, and the Coinbase mission&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;An entrepreneurial mindset with the ability to succeed in a fast-paced environment&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-unorderedListItem public-DraftStyleDefault-reset public-DraftStyleDefault-depth0 public-DraftStyleDefault-listLTR&quot; data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;8k6a2-0-0&quot;&gt;Fluent in English and based in Toronto or Ottawa&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with general management, market launcher, or strategy and operations roles in high-growth start-ups, tech, finance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in the Crypto industry (expertise not a prerequisite but willingness to learn and enthusiasm essential)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;French speaking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;euo8b-0-0&quot;&gt;ID: GP927-1-CN&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Transparency Notice: &lt;/strong&gt;The target annual salary for this position can range as detailed below. Full time offers from Coinbase also include target bonus + target equity + benefits (including medical, dental, and vision).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Pay Range:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$185,500&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$185,500 CAD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As the Product Manager for Coinbase in the Netherlands, you will take the helm of our product and engineering team in the local market. Your primary responsibilities will involve spearheading growth initiatives and fine-tuning the Coinbase experience for Dutch consumers, ensuring a tailored product-market fit. This position requires close collaboration with cross-functional teams, including Engineering, Design, Marketing, and Customer Support. Your main emphasis will be on boosting revenue and fostering user growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing (ie. job duties):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; To be completed by all business teams except Eng.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own product development / localisation from conception to launch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with engineering, design and other cross-functional teams to develop and steer the local product roadmap&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and analyse metrics to guide product development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Align teams on a shared vision and steer execution on that vision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate progress on initiatives to cross-functional partners and executive leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you (ie. job requirements):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; To be completed by all business teams except Eng.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of product software management experience with a proven track record of successfully driving growth initiatives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional interpersonal communication, relationship management and organisational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structured problem solver and strong analytical skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Both strategic and tactical thinking. You have strong intellect, a broad perspective, and the confidence to engage with senior leaders across multiple disciplines&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated passion for cryptocurrency, financial markets, and the Coinbase mission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self starter with an entrepreneurial mindset that has the ability to succeed in a fast-paced ever changing environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Native Dutch speaker, fluent English and based in the Netherlands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with general management, market launcher, or strategy and operations roles in high-growth start-ups, tech, finance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in the Crypto industry (expertise not a prerequisite but willingness to learn and enthusiasm essential)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in a second (non english) widely spoken European language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is committed to diversity in its workforce and is proud to be an Equal Opportunity Employer.&amp;nbsp; All qualified applicants will receive consideration for employment without regard to race, color, religion, creed, gender, national origin, age, disability, veteran status, sex, gender expression or identity, sexual orientation or any other basis protected by applicable law. Coinbase will also consider for employment qualified applicants with criminal histories in a manner consistent with applicable federal, state and local law. &amp;nbsp;For US applicants, you may view&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/ofccp/pdf/pay-transp_English_unformattedESQA508c.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Pay Transparency&lt;/a&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.dol.gov/sites/dolgov/files/WHD/legacy/files/eppac.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Employee Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://www.eeoc.gov/sites/default/files/2022-10/22-088_EEOC_KnowYourRights_10_20.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Know Your Rights&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;notices by clicking on their corresponding links.&amp;nbsp; Additionally, Coinbase participates in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://static-assets.coinbase.com/e-verify.pdf&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot; data-remove-tab-index=&quot;true&quot;&gt;E-Verify program&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in certain locations, as required by law.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Coinbase is also committed to providing reasonable accommodations to individuals with disabilities. If you need a reasonable accommodation because of a disability for any part of the employment process, please complete this&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class=&quot;c-link&quot; href=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1aJ6-BSPwE5X5Dq7fJ9JixWF0_dRiNfrpMnn1NkvdRiA/edit?ts=62901076&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;intake form&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to let us know the nature of your request and your contact information.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; For quick access to screen reading technology compatible with this site &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/chromevox/kgejglhpjiefppelpmljglcjbhoiplfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;click here to download&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; a free compatible screen reader &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chromevox.com/tutorial/&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;(free step by step tutorial can be found here)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Global Data Privacy Notice for Job Candidates and Applicants&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Depending on your location, the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) may regulate the way we manage the data of job applicants. Our full notice outlining how data will be processed as part of the application procedure for applicable locations is available &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/applicant_privacy_notice&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;By submitting your application, you are agreeing to our use and processing of your data as required. For US applicants only, by submitting your application you are agreeing to arbitration of disputes as outlined &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.coinbase.com/legal/application-arbitration-agreement&quot;&gt;here.&lt;/a&gt; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;At Coinbase, our mission is to&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/our-mission-strategy-and-culture-18a92a3bb0fa&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;increase economic freedom around the world&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;, and we couldn’t do this without hiring the best people. We’re a group of hard-working overachievers who are deeply focused on building the future of finance and Web3 for our users across the globe, whether they’re trading, storing, staking or using crypto. Know those people who always lead the group project? That’s us.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;There are a few things we look for across all hires we make at Coinbase, regardless of role or team. First, we look for candidates who will thrive in a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/culture-at-coinbase-f0e1c2a99aff&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;culture&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; like ours, where we default to trust, embrace feedback, and disrupt ourselves. Second, we expect all employees to commit to our&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.coinbase.com/coinbase-is-a-mission-focused-company-af882df8804&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;mission-focused approach&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; to our work. Finally, we seek people who are excited to learn about and live crypto, because those are the folks who enjoy the intense moments in our sprint and recharge work culture. We’re a remote-first company looking to hire the absolute best talent all over the world.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ready to #LiveCrypto? Who you are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve got positive energy. You’re optimistic about the future and determined to get there.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’re never tired of learning. You want to be a pro in bleeding edge tech like DeFi, NFTs, DAOs, and Web 3.0.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You appreciate direct communication. You’re both an active communicator and an eager listener - because let’s face it, you can’t have one without the other. You’re cool with candid feedback and see every setback as an opportunity to grow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You can pivot on the fly. Crypto is constantly evolving, so our priorities do, too. What you worked on last month may not be what you work on today, and that excites you. You’re not looking for a boring job.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You have a “can do” attitude. Our teams create high-quality work on quick timelines. Owning a problem doesn’t scare you, but rather empowers you to take 100% responsibility for achieving our mission.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You want to be part of a winning team. We’re stronger together, and you’re a person who embraces being pushed out of your comfort zone. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The mission of the Platform Product Group engineers is to build a trusted, scalable and compliant platform to operate with speed, efficiency and quality. Our teams build and maintain the platforms critical to the existence of Coinbase. There are many teams that make up this group which include Product Foundations (i.e. Identity, Payment, Risk, Proofing &amp;amp; Regulatory, Finhub), Machine Learning, Customer Experience, and Infrastructure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;6rt44-0-0&quot;&gt;The CB-GPT team’s charter is to build a secure, seamless, and state-of-the-art LLM platform which will enable both technical and non-technical teams to unlock the power of LLMs for bespoke needs at Coinbase. As the Product Manager for LLM Applications, you will be responsible for accelerating the adoption and impact of our LLM platform (CB-GPT) by building new LLM-backed applications that improve efficiency and unlock new capabilities for teams across the company.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div data-block=&quot;true&quot; data-editor=&quot;dukh8&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;4iede-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;4iede-0-0&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;4iede-0-0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll be doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr&quot; data-offset-key=&quot;4iede-0-0&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead development of our&amp;nbsp; LLM “Assistant” UI features that make it simple and safe for employees to leverage LLMs. Build new capabilities such as a chrome extension or Slackbot to increase adoption of the CB-GPT service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conceptualize novel ways to apply LLM across Coinbase business units. Work with stakeholders to validate high-value opportunities and build minimally viable products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work cross-functionally with teams across the company such as legal, compliance, and marketing&amp;nbsp; to develop customized LLM solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Measure and communicate impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we look for in you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of&amp;nbsp; PM experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in building simple and delightful user interfaces&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong interest in the LLM space and how LLMs can drive efficiency and innovation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional interpersonal communication, relationship management and organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep analytical, prioritization and problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience working in software product management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated passion for cryptocurrency, financial markets, and the Coinbase mission&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An entrepreneurial mindset with the ability to succeed in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Large Language Models&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-offset-key=&quot;euo8b-0-0&quot;&gt;ID: G2026&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Commitment to Equal Opportunity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
