&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;You have at least 5+ years of experience in software engineering and at least 3 years of experience in developing web apps and shipping user-facing features with JavaScript and modern, component-based JS frameworks like React.&lt;/li&gt;
